<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Password Updated - {{siteName}}</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .header {
      background-color: #2e7d32;
      padding: 25px 20px;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
    }

    .header h1 {
      color: #ffffff;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .content {
      padding: 30px 20px;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
    }

    .alert-box {
      background-color: #e8f5e9;
      border-left: 4px solid #2e7d32;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }

    .footer {
      background-color: #e8f5e9;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #666666;
    }

    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background-color: #388e3c;
      color: white !important;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>Password Changed Successfully</h1>
  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <p>Hello {{firstName}},</p>

    <div class="alert-box">
      <p><strong>This is a security notification:</strong> Your {{siteName}} account password was recently changed.</p>
    </div>

    <p>If you initiated this change, no further action is required.</p>

    <p><strong>If you didn't change your password:</strong></p>
    <ol>
      <li>Reset your password immediately using the link below</li>
      <li>Contact our support team</li>
      <li>Check your account for suspicious activity</li>
    </ol>

    <center>
      <a href="https://{{domain}}/reset-password" class="button">Reset Password</a>
    </center>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    <p>For your security, this notification was sent to all email addresses associated with your account.</p>
    <p>Â© {{year}} {{siteName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
    <p>
      <a href="https://{{domain}}/security" style="color: #2e7d32;">Security Tips</a> |
      <a href="https://{{domain}}/contact" style="color: #2e7d32;">Contact Support</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</body>

</html>